&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Feedzai, we&#39;re building a world of safer money. A world where financial institutions move faster than criminals. Where the payments that fund real lives through salaries, savings, and businesses are protected in real time. We use trusted AI to detect and prevent financial crime, fraud, and money laundering at scale: the world&#39;s top banks, payment networks, and acquirers trust our technology to safeguard more than one billion consumers and $9 trillion in payment volume every year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feedzai is a Series D company and has raised $282M to date. With a valuation of $2 billion, our technology protects 1 billion consumers and 90 billion transactions each year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Product Team&lt;/strong&gt; builds products to disrupt the financial crime industry from a data-led approach. We partner with our clients using a holistic lens and have result-driven solutions to manage financial risk with a cloud-first platform and a world-class UX interface. Being part of this team, you have a voice in planning, strategizing, and challenging the status quo. Your thoughts and ideas are valued. Our fast-paced and open environment encourages us to lean in, try new things, and discover our potential. We define and act on what could be in tomorrow&#39;s world, not on what is today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Product Manager &lt;/strong&gt;with a strong customer focus and a passion for building great products to join us in this exciting journey and orchestrate the definition and execution of Feedzai’s Digital Trust Product vision &amp;amp; strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a highly motivated and enthusiastic Product Manager at Feedzai you will play a crucial role in the development of our Digital Trust solution. You’ll be working across Research and Labs, Engineering, Data Science, Business and Design, and Feedzai customers. Understanding both the technical and business side of Feedzai’s Digital Trust product solution, you will be responsible for developing technologically advanced capabilities that utilise device, behavioural biometric and cyber threat intelligence signals to build out a persistent re-identification of customer trust / customer threats, and autonomously drive and scale the Digital Trust roadmap.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a self-starter with an ability to think strategically, act pragmatically, and have the tenacity, energy and passion to innovate and implement change within the time and resource constraints of a quickly growing startup environment. Furthermore, serving as an advisor to cross-functional and customer-facing teams within Feedzai, and customers themselves, you will be responsible for ensuring that the Digital Trust solution is responsive to changing technology standards and real-world problems. Keeping up-to-date with new threats, new trends and new techniques in signal gathering and processing you will help drive the development of Digital Trust capabilities around Network, Device and Malware related analysis and detection, and help ensure their practical real-world application and usability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Day to Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and analysis of key risks within the digital fraud landscape; analysing, developing, building and testing new detection capabilities that utilise data and risk signals from device, behavioural biometric and cyber threat intelligence to recognise user persistency, threat indicators and behavioural anomalies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop product scope and definition for features on the Digital Trust product roadmap, bridging gaps across Product, Platform, Data Science, and Operations to ensure long-term scalability and t

