&lt;p&gt;You will play a key role in ensuring the scalability, security, and performance of our Digital Trust solutions, which help financial institutions detect anomalies, assess risk, and protect users from digital fraud. &lt;strong&gt;This role requires strong technical leadership, stakeholder management, and the ability to drive a team towards innovation and execution.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should be an engineer at heart who enjoys solving complex technical challenges while mentoring and developing top talent. Your ability to align technical execution with business goals will be crucial in shaping the future of Digital Trust at Feedzai.&lt;/p&gt;
