&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Product Management to transform requirements and ideas into working software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead by example, fostering a culture of technical excellence, ownership, and collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical leadership, guiding the team in architecture, design, and code reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the planning, execution, and success of technical projects&lt;/li&gt;
