&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting the planning and execution of regional marketing programs, including trade shows, conferences, hosted events, and regional campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage campaign logistics, timelines, vendors, budgets, and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on performance and ROI for all field activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with sales and ADR teams to align marketing activities with pipeline goals and territory priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with partner marketing initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
