&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting or working alongside senior marketing leaders, with the ability to take strategic direction and run independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong project management and organizational skills, with the ability to juggle multiple initiatives simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative mindset and the ability to work cross-functionally across marketing, sales, partnerships in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
