&lt;p&gt;The Industry Relations Intern will play an important role within the Marketing team, driving collaborative initiatives across internal departments and external bodies. This role involves engaging with banking and other industry associations, academic institutions, regulatory agencies, and governmental entities. You will gain hands-on expertise with essential platforms such as Salesforce, G Suite, Vixio, Klue, and Monday.com to streamline these efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Day to Day:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become a power user of Marketing Automation tools like Monday.com and Salesforce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct market research on prospective partners while facilitating internal project coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with procurement workflows for industry relations in coordination with finance to maintain budget integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and evaluate initiative outcomes through the creation of automated performance reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner effectively with our regional marketing colleagues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee a comprehensive calendar to log all engagement activities and interaction specifics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
