&lt;li&gt;Cleaning that data and validating that it is correct;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preprocessing the data, usually by using a mixture of shell scripts and a programming language such as Python, Java, Scala, etc&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Iteratively computing features and tuning parameters to improve the quality of the model;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicating your findings to the project manager and assisting him/her in decision making on the Data Science part of the project;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work together with key stakeholders (data scientists, engineers, risk managers) from our clients;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with other parts of the organization (Product, Research, etc.) to improve processes, best practices and tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
