&lt;li&gt;MSc or PhD in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Statistics, Applied Mathematics, Physics or related field;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in Machine Learning (training and testing, avoiding overfit, etc.);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Big Data technologies such as Spark, Hadoop and related;&lt;/li&gt;
